sleep is involved? Further, and pivotal, is a distinction about when
the dreaming referred to occurred or is occurring or will occur. The
basic disagreements have, it is probably fair to say, their roots in
the temporal relation of Dante's dreaming. (1) Either Dante has been
'dreaming' from the beginning of this special experience, as might be
indicated by ^Inferno~ I.11, where Dante admits he was full of sleep
